<p>Hi <%= @recipient.person&.first_name || "there" %>,</p>

<p><strong><%= @person.name %></strong> has removed themselves from the talent pool for <strong><%= @production.name %></strong>.</p>

<% if @groups.any? %>
<p>The following groups were also removed:</p>
<ul>
  <% @groups.each do |group| %>
    <li><%= group.name %></li>
  <% end %>
</ul>
<% end %>

<p>They will no longer be considered for future scheduling, but any existing assignments remain in place.</p>

<p>
  <a href="<%= manage_casting_talent_pool_url(@production) %>" style="display: inline-block; padding: 12px 24px; background-color: #ec4899; color: white; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: 500;">
    View Talent Pool
  </a>
</p>

<p style="color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px;">
  You're receiving this because you have notifications enabled for <%= @production.name %>.
</p>
